Class ViewCEOReportsController

java.lang.Object
gui.ViewCEOReportsController
All Implemented Interfaces:
IControl, javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class ViewCEOReportsController extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable, IControl
Controller for the CEO Reports Page in the application. This class manages the display and interaction with various reports including order reports, income reports, and performance charts.
Version:
5.0
